biography: Thomas Reifenberger works as an IT Consultant for the Munich based consulting company TNG Technology Consulting GmbH. Before joining the company in 2012 studied physics at the Technical University of Munich. Since then he worked for various customers in different sectors – with his technical focus areas being Java, Perl, Groovy & Python. Besides that he is involved in the company's hardware hacking team, where he is mainly working with IoT projects. Besides other tasks, he is involved in deployment automation, Linux administration and networking for the team.
